trans-unit.source: Manages the placement of breakpoints for a debugging process.
trans-unit.target: Administrerer plasseringen av stoppunkt for en prosess for feilsøking.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Debug.DebuggerService"></xref> class with the specified editing context.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Debug.DebuggerService"> </xref> klassen med den angitte redigering konteksten.

trans-unit.source: The activity designer contextual state.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitet Spørringsutformer kontekstavhengig tilstanden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the current scope of execution in the source file.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir gjeldende område for kjøring i kildefilen.

trans-unit.source: A position in the source file that marks the start of execution.
trans-unit.target: En posisjon i kildefilen som angir starten på kjøring.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the current location of execution.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir gjeldende plassering for kjøring.

trans-unit.source: A location in the source file.
trans-unit.target: En plassering i kildefilen.

trans-unit.source: Deletes a breakpoint from its location in the source file.
trans-unit.target: Sletter et stoppunkt fra plassering i kildefilen.

trans-unit.source: A location in the source file.
trans-unit.target: En plassering i kildefilen.

trans-unit.source: Ensures that the debugger service is visible.
trans-unit.target: Sikrer at tjenesten debugger er synlig.

trans-unit.source: A location in the source file.
trans-unit.target: En plassering i kildefilen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a list of the latest breakpoint locations.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en liste over siste stoppunkt plasseringer.

trans-unit.source: A list of breakpoints of type <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Debug.BreakpointInfo.SourceLocation*> culled from the source file.
trans-unit.target: En liste over stoppunkt av typen <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Debug.BreakpointInfo.SourceLocation*>culled fra kildefilen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Debug.BreakpointInfo.SourceLocation*>

trans-unit.source: Returns an exact source file location based on the start and end line numbers of the activity in its serialized XAML form.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en nøyaktig kildeplassering basert på start- og avslutte linje tallene av aktiviteten i den serialiserte XAML-formen.

trans-unit.source: A source file location known to be inexact.
trans-unit.target: En kilde-filplassering vet er unøyaktig.

trans-unit.source: An exact location in the source file.
trans-unit.target: En nøyaktig plassering i kildefilen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the source file name in the viewer is hidden.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om kildenavnet i hendelseslisten er skjult.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the source file name is hidden; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis kilden filnavn er skjulte. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Inserts a new breakpoint of the specified type at the specified location.
trans-unit.target: Setter inn en ny stoppunkt av angitt type på den angitte plasseringen.

trans-unit.source: The location in the source file that receives the new breakpoint.
trans-unit.target: Plasseringen i kildefilen som mottar nye stoppunkt.

trans-unit.source: The type of the breakpoint; for example, None, Enabled, Bounded, or Conditional.
trans-unit.target: Hva slags stoppunkt; for eksempel ingen, aktivert, Bounded eller betinget.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether debugging is the current state.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om feilsøking er den gjeldende tilstanden.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if debugging is the current state; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis feilsøking den gjeldende tilstanden. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Resets breakpoints and prepares for breakpoint refresh.
trans-unit.target: Tilbakestiller stoppunkt og Klargjør for stoppunkt oppdatering.

trans-unit.source: Gets the currently selected location from the designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter den valgte plasseringen fra designer.

trans-unit.source: The position in the source file that is currently selected.
trans-unit.target: Plasseringen i kildefilen som er valgt.

trans-unit.source: Updates the appearance of a specified breakpoint to show the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Oppdaterer utseendet til et angitt stoppunkt å vise den angitte typen.

trans-unit.source: The location of the breakpoint to update.
trans-unit.target: Plasseringen av stoppunkt å oppdatere.

trans-unit.source: A new breakpoint type from the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Debug.BreakpointTypes"></xref> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: En ny stoppunkt type fra den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Debug.BreakpointTypes"> </xref> opplisting.

trans-unit.source: Collects the new mapping of model item and breakpoints from SourceLocationMapping.
trans-unit.target: Samler inn ny tilordning av modellelementet og stoppunkt fra SourceLocationMapping.

trans-unit.source: A list of model item and breakpoint pairs.
trans-unit.target: En liste over modellen elementet og stoppunkt par.
